comment: Gibson (CHI) makes contact with Felton's (DAL) arm that affects his drive to the basket and shot attempt.
Pachulia (DAL) maintains a legal guarding position as Mirotic (CHI) starts his drive to the basket.
Butler (CHI) makes contact with Felton (DAL) that affects his RSBQ.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling that Butler (CHI) was behind the three-point line on his made shot was upheld.
Pachulia (DAL) and Gasol (CHI) make incidental contact as they engage to grab the rebound.
Chicago does not inbound the ball in less than 5 seconds.
Hinrich (CHI) commits a take foul on Felton (DAL).
